title: PMS 2.0 776 -Thursday Night Football Recap, NFL Week 9 Preview/Picks With AJ Hawk LIVE From The ThunderDome
description: On today’s show, Pat joins AJ Hawk, and the boys live from the set of College GameDay in Athens, Georgia as they chat about last night’s Thursday Night Football game between the Texans and Eagles, The Athens tailgates scene, and all things going on with the NFL including their upcoming expectations for week 9. Pat and AJ make their picks against the spread (1.14.46-1.32.48) right before they welcome in the General Manager for the Buffalo Bills Brandon Beane (1.33.04-1.46.10). Make sure you subscribe to youtube.com/thepatmcafeeshow to watch the show. We appreciate the hell out of all you. See you on Overreaction Monday, cheers.
